yay -S --needed gst-libav gst-plugins-base gst-plugins-good lib32-gst-plugins-good gst-plugins-bad lib32-gst-plugins-bad gst-plugins-ugly lib32-gst-plugins-ugly gst-plugin-pipewire gstreamer ffmpeg libde265 libdvdcss libdvdread libdvdnav a52dec faac faad2 flac jasper lame libdca libdv libmad libmpeg2 libtheora libvorbis libvpx opencore-amr openjpeg2 speex x264 x265 xvidcore wavpack chromium-widevine
```


## 11. Установить основные пакеты:

```
sudo pacman -S --needed base-devel nano reflector sudo curl net-tools wget git openssh networkmanager rsync unzip zip inxi fish fastfetch amd-ucode linux-firmware
```

