yay -S --needed waybar hyprpaper xdg-desktop-portal-hyprland hyprpolkitagent hyprsysteminfo nwg-look kora-icon-theme dracula-gtk-theme swaync pipewire pipewire-pulse pipewire-alsa lib32-pipewire wireplumber hyprshot slurp grim hyprland-qtutils hyprgraphics  hyprwayland-scanner aquamarine hyprutils hyprlock qt6-svg qt6-declarative qt5-quickcontrols2 wlogout nwg-drawer networkmanager gnome-calendar thunar q pavucontrol sddm ninja gcc cmake meson libxcb xcb-proto xcb-util xcb-util-keysyms libxfixes libx11 libxcomposite libxrender libxcursor pixman wayland-protocols cairo pango libxkbcommon xcb-util-wm xorg-xwayland libinput libliftoff libdisplay-info cpio tomlplusplus hyprlang hyprcursor hyprwayland-scanner xcb-util-errors hyprutils glaze hyprgraphics aquamarine re2 hyprland-qtutils qt5ct qt6ct qt5-wayland qt6-wayland lib32-pipewire vimix-cursors swappy wl-clipboard wl-clip-persist cliphist tela-circle-icon-theme-all winbox nwg-displays gtk4-layer-shell polkit-gnome xdg-user-dirs gvfs-mtp gvfs-afc gvfs-smb udisks2 udiskie gtk2
```

## 13. Установить "рабочий" софт для Hyprland

 -  Файловый менеджер - thunar (gvfs + tumbler)
 -  Терминал - ghostty
 -  Терминал стиль - starship
 -  Текстовый редактор - mousepad
 -  Запуск приложений -  walker
 -  Плеер - mpv
 -  Картинки - loupe
 -  Офис - OnlyOffice
 -  Архиватор - xarchiver
 -  Pdf - papers
 -  Torrent - qbittorrent-qt5 ([тема](https://github.com/catppuccin/qbittorrent/releases))
 -  Диски - [gnome-disk-utility](https://github.com/GNOME/gnome-disk-utility)
 -  Системный монитор - [Mission Center](https://gitlab.com/mission-center-devs/mission-center)
 -  FTP клиент - [Filezilla](https://filezilla-project.org/)
 -  Браузер vivaldi
 -  Редактор заметок - [Obsidian](https://github.com/obsidianmd/obsidian-releases)
 -  Редактор шрифтов  - gnome-font-viewer
-  Калькулятор - gnome-calculator


```
yay -S --needed ghostty starship gvfs tumbler mousepad walker-bin mpv loupe onlyoffice-bin xarchiver papers qbittorrent-qt5  gnome-disk-utility mission-center filezilla vivaldi obsidian zoxide mcfly visual-studio-code-bin telegram-desktop gnome-font-viewer gnome-calculator thunar-archive-plugin thunar-media-tags-plugin
```  

Визуальное изменение громкости 

[Syshud](https://github.com/System64fumo/syshud)

